<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97190793921642></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97190793921642><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=4&mid=97190793921642>RE: What can I do to survive in groups as a bard?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?id=2116><span id= >Amadeos</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>2 posts</td></tr>
